                <h4>What is a Stock Screener?</h4>
            </a>

        </div>
        <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse in">
            <div class="panel-body">
                <p>  A stock screener is a tool that investors can use to sort and filter stocks based on a set of different user-defined criterias.</p>
                <p>The Value Screener provides several screeners, all based on value investing criterias, allowing the user to find cheap companies with good fundamentals.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
